-- Trading Turkey's Bank Asya shares halted until 0840 GMT-exchange
-- 
-- Fri Sep 26, 2014 04:17AM EDT
-- None



ISTANBUL, Sept 26 (Reuters) - Trading in shares of Turkey's Islamic lender Bank Asya <ASYAB.IS> was halted temporarily for a second time on Friday due to volatility in share price, Borsa Istanbul said in a filing.

